text: Sinaamak Yallak kalah numtin- wellitte yallitteh haysitaah Yallat Agleh tet haa maray tet yakcineeh yaynabe yan, moominiin Yalla kah kicniih kah taynabe innah, yeemeneh yan mari Yallah kacanuh wohuk lafitak Raaqa, Addunyâ manol koroosannut isi nafsi yudlume mari Akeeral digaalâ gibda yable waqdi aaxaginnay, diggah duddaa kee Qande inkih Yalli-lem Aaxaguk yenen Diggah Yalli gibdi digaala- le
